cs.SI, cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.CC, cs.SD 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on online social networks and their reward systems. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also likely as the paper discusses users' motivations and behaviors in using online social networks and their badge systems. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper touches on the impact of badge systems on users' online activities and contributions. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.SD (Software Engineering) are less likely but still possible categories as the paper may involve some computational and software engineering aspects in designing and implementing badge systems.
